\mu_1\times \mu_2
\phi
2\pi
 \phi(\xi_1,\xi_2) = \int_{\mathbb R^2} e^{2\pi i x\cdot \xi} \,dx_1\,dx_2  = \int_{\mathbb R} e^{2\pi i x_1 \xi_1} \,dx_1 \cdot \int_{\mathbb R} e^{2\pi i x_2 \xi_2} \,dx_2 = \hat \mu_1(\xi_1)\hat \mu_2(\xi_2) 
